Enum Class SQLiteColumnTypeResolver

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SQLiteColumnTypeResolver>
dimstyl.orm.internal.sql.resolver.SQLiteColumnTypeResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
ColumnTypeResolver, Serializable, Comparable<SQLiteColumnTypeResolver>, Constable
enum SQLiteColumnTypeResolver extends Enum<SQLiteColumnTypeResolver> implements ColumnTypeResolver
Singleton enum implementation of ColumnTypeResolver for the SQLite database.

This resolver maps Java data types to their corresponding SQLite SQL data types based on the official SQLite documentation.

It supports the following Java-to-SQLite type mappings:

  • String → TEXT
  • boolean, Boolean → INTEGER
  • short, Short → INTEGER
  • int, Integer → INTEGER
  • long, Long → INTEGER
  • float, Float → REAL
  • double, Double → REAL
